    "body": "this is a limitation of contract impersonating because we need to bypass EIP-3607\r\nby temporarily removing the contract code of the impersonated contract.\r\n\r\nthe code is added back if you stop impersonating the contract though\r\n\r\nwe need to document this limitation if it's not already mentioned in the book",
